fig.label: Figure 3.

caption.p: Differentially expressed genes (DEGs) GO term and PPI analysis

fig.attrib: (A) Venn diagram illustrating unique and common DEGs in MEFD3plu/MEFD3min and MEFD5plu/MEFD5min based on statistical significance cut-off p-adj<0.05. (B) GO term analysis (biological processes) of the common DEGs between MEFD3plu/MEFD3min and MEFD5plu/MEFD5min showing fat cell differentiation to have the highest enrichment significance. Number of genes displayed adjacently to in each enrichment bar chart. False dependent rate, represented as P-adj values, are normalized to -log10(P-adj).
